import React from 'react';
import { Button, Typography, Container, Box} from '@material-ui/core';
import Table from "./table";
import TextField from "./textfields"
import Toolbar from "./toolbar"
import BottomToolbar from "./bottomtoolbar"
import Snackbars from "./snackbars"



function App() {

  return (

  <Container maxWidth="sm" display="flex" justifyContent="center">
    <Toolbar></Toolbar>
    
      <Typography variant="h4" gutterBottom>
        MyApp
      </Typography>
      <TextField>
      </TextField>
     
      <Button color="primary" variant="contained">BUTTON</Button>  
      <Button color="secondary" variant="outlined">BUTTON</Button>
      
      
      <Box mt={3} mb={3}>
        <Table />
      </Box>
      <Box> <Snackbars></Snackbars></Box>
      <BottomToolbar></BottomToolbar>
   </Container>
  )
  
}

export default App;
